434
00:39:41,590 --> 00:39:42,674
Hayır.

435
00:39:43,800 --> 00:39:44,635
Hayır!

436
00:40:11,745 --> 00:40:12,788
Sağ ol kızım.

437
00:40:14,706 --> 00:40:16,500
Hey.

438
00:40:19,628 --> 00:40:20,504
İyi misin?

